{"tid":2008774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息指再多一名早前出院的確診者第二度呈陽性反應","createTime":"2020-05-09T09:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T09:47:02.000Z","uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4ce096ab87cc02b926f160862d8f6ae65133e4a6","tid":2008774,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:31:31.000Z","msg":"消息指再多一名早前出院的確診者「復陽」<br />\n09.05.2020 17:28<br />\n<br />\n本港今日沒有新增的新型冠狀病毒個案，是連續20日沒本地病例，累計維持1044宗。醫管局指，過去一日再多7名病人康復出院。但消息指，再有早前出院的個案「復陽」。一名上月25日出院的33歲女病人，出現咳嗽的症狀後昨晚再入院，深喉唾液樣本初步對病毒呈陽性反應，現時在醫院留醫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286301&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1286301%26csid%3D261_341&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=2531fc16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286301&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"6a07bcd050f381fcd1a3549ddfe1ef923c551fc1","tid":2008774,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:32:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4nzUThz8BvI&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=83cec3a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC7YbpoujZlw&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=62fd2557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw</a>"},{"pid":"f662adc0c467c00490aacff2416669d5abcb0dd9","tid":2008774,"uid":81500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"政府：復陽唔計新個案"},{"pid":"c54fec2b01ee64b19d79c7d5bfd71a6dc7fe047f","tid":2008774,"uid":18999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05